skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: animal quiz
des:
This skills tells user about the name of the animal group you asked.
To invoke the skill say open "animal quiz". after that alexa welcomes you with the greeting message.then it asks you to say any animal name. after telling the animal name to alexa it tells user about the name of that particular animal group.user may say , for example: "what is the group of cat called?" , alexa responds by saying "the name of the cat group is called as clowder".after this it stops or you can ask more.
